            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5737182-kate?shelf=favourites-read-in-2017">favourites-read-in-2017</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5737182-kate?shelf=out-in-2017-and-read">out-in-2017-and-read</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2005085947" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9705791407069668770">A light read but nevertheless enjoyable. 3.5 stars.<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
